<div class="w-11/12 md:w-5/6 mx-auto w-full py-8 px-3 md:px-0">
  <h1 class="text-4xl">No Salesforce!</h1>
  <div class="my-8">
    <%= image_tag "no_salesforce.jpg" %>
  </div>
  <div class="text-xl">
  <p>
    Salesforce has gotten bloated and forgotten what it was originally supposed to do. It's become a tool for executive's micromangement and performative reporting instead of helping those on the ground actually connect with customers.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6">
    Salesforce pioneered the SaaS model, and has been at the forefront of taking it way too far. Businesses pay tens or hundreds of thousands&emdash;some millions!&emdash;on a tool that should be relatively simple.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6">
    This project restores the original intent of the CRM&emdash;to help people form real relationships with their customers!
  </p>
</div>
